What is a conflict?
====================================================

</br>

1. Minor Conflict: At least 25 battle deaths/year

2. Major Conflict/Civil War: At least 1,000 battle deaths/year

3. Type: Inter-state / Civil / Communal

4. Condition: At least 5% loss on both sides


